comment: Carroll (TOR) sets the screen on Morris (DET) and the two players briefly engage and separate.
Morris (DET) makes contact with the ball and DeRozan's (TOR) hand that is part of the ball and Smith (DET) makes incidental contact with DeRozan that does not affect his SQBR. CNC
Smith (DET) makes incidental contact with Carroll (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR. Video
[Detectable with stop watch] Nogueira (TOR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
DeRozan (TOR) makes contact with the ball and Caldwell-Pope's (DET) hand that is part of the ball on the drive to the basket.
Lowry (TOR) remains in bounds along the sideline prior to his drive to the basket.
[Observable in enhanced video] LATR shows Valanciunas (TOR) never fully clears the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
[Detectable with stop watch] Morris (DET) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Caldwell-Pope (DET) extends his leg on the jump shot attempt and initiates the marginal contact with Lowry (TOR).
Valanciunas (TOR) dislodges Drummond (DET), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Morris (DET) maintains legal guarding position on DeRozan (TOR) on the perimeter.
Carroll (TOR) sets the screen on Morris (DET) and the two players briefly engage and separate.
Morris (DET) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] LO SLA shows Lowry (TOR) move his pivot foot.
Caldwell-Pope (DET) makes contact with Lowry (TOR) that affects his SQBR.
Morris (DET) grabs DeRozan's (TOR) jersey and makes contact to the body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Drummond (DET) and Valanciunas (TOR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Dedmon (SAS) makes incidental contact with Hernangomez (NYK) that does not affect his SQBR.
Anthony (NYK) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Leonard (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Anthony (NYK) legally contests Leonard's (SAS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Anthony (NYK) makes marginal contact with Green (SAS) on the screen.
Green (SAS) and Anthony (NYK) briefly engage establishing post position.
[Observable in enhanced video] Dedmon (SAS) moves his pivot foot heel to toe.
Dedmon (SAS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Hernangomez (NYK) makes incidental contact with Green (SAS) during reblounding.
Green (SAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Rose (NYK) that does not affect his SQBR.
Leonard (SAS) initiates the contact with Porzingis (NYK) on the drive to the basket and Porzingis blocks the shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of NYK possession is overturned and SAS are awarded possession.
Anthony (NYK) makes contact with the ball after it is outside of the cylinder.
Ginobili (SAS) commits a take foul on Anthony (NYK).
Green (SAS) commits a take foul on Rose (NYK).
Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on Thomas (NYK) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Porzingis (NYK) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Leonard (SAS) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
